 * 20250131 Frank Tate:
 * The purpose of this AL is to pull recon audti data from the ISIM DB for a specified day and
 * service, manipulate it, then write it to an html file (/tmp/audit.html - change as needed).
 * 
 * The goal for HTTPServerConnector was to make this a web-accessible solution where users could
